{"TopicId":133694,"ForumId":25,"TopicTitle":"Totally balanced challenge","CreatedByName":"WOLVSAid","CreatedById":144612,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-07T18:58:01Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"WOLVSAid","CreatedById":144612,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-07T18:58:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKSP 1.0.5\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEver good at building airplane / rocket\u00A0?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow about balancing it for a change\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EThe challenge :\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe goal is to pitch to max of 10 degree and \u003Cu\u003Estay stable for more then 10 Second without falling below 0 degree\u003C/u\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn other words you cannot use SAS or mechjeb or any mod that control the craft, ( no triming either )\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cu\u003ELook mom, I\u0027m flying with\u00A0No hands\u003C/u\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ERating :\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere\u0027s no easy mode for this at it is hard enough already so,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTo be\u00A0qualified\u00A0for the challenge you should last more then \u003Cu\u003E10 second in stable flight and the rating will be based on total weight of your craft\u003C/u\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EDa rulezzz :\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe challenge is open for all mods and all cheats, Feel free to do it in anyway you want\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHere\u0027s my example and try :\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSkylon M\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/Hq9dJ1KrhM8?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cu\u003EPlease submit a video or screenshots on this thread to enter the challenge\u003C/u\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCheck me out \u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/user/WOLVSAid\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehere\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-03-07T19:09:59Z\u0022 title=\u002203/07/2016 07:09  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 7, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by WOLVSAid\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EAdded triming to the rules\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tex_NL","CreatedById":58254,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-07T19:03:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222446365\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022133694\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221457377081\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022144612\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022WOLVSAid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 minutes ago, WOLVSAid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere\u0027s no easy mode for this at it is hard enough already so,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSorry but there is no \u0027hard mode\u0027 either because this is incredibly easy. Simply use the [Alt]\u002B[W / S] to trim your pitch.\u003Cbr\u003E\nAny reasonably designed plane can be kept level with proper trimming for an extended period of time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-03-07T19:05:44Z\u0022 title=\u002203/07/2016 07:05  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 7, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Tex_NL\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"WOLVSAid","CreatedById":144612,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-07T19:09:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222446372\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022133694\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221457377416\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002258254\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Tex_NL\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 minutes ago, Tex_NL said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSimply use the [Alt]\u002B[W / S] to trim your pitch.\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere is / should be no control at all, no trim no SAS or anything,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThx for your concern, I will update the post now.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}